# Research captures of the live PBCC site — reference only, never shipped.
# See FETCH_PLAN.md § Legal hygiene.
research/captures/

# Raw deep-research dossiers (Claude investigations, source-sensitive notes).
# We protect the research methodology by keeping the raw artefacts local.
# Only the extracted, sourced facts — promoted into FACTS.md and the typed
# source registry — are committed. The README explaining this convention
# is exempted so future contributors can see the pipeline.
research/raw/*
!research/raw/README.md

# Get A Life podcast transcripts and extractions: survivor testimony and
# private member names that, per research/getalife/REPORT.md, never ship.
# Kept local; only sourced facts promoted into FACTS.md and the registry ship.
research/getalife/

